n records on postage, registration of mail and packages.</p><p>The position coordinates all office equipment shipping, including FedEx and UPS packages.</p><p>Order packing supplies and maintain inventory of common packing supplies and boxes.</p><p>Assist with procuring general office supplies stored in the mailroom.</p><p>Stocking and maintaining inventory levels of all office supplies. Order and maintain stock of preprinted PSAV stationary supplies.</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Required Skills</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Competencies</p><p>Initiative</p><p>Production Efficiency</p><p>Exceeds Customer Expectations</p><p>Flexibility</p><p>Teamwork</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Physical Requirements</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Team members must be able to meet the physical demands above in order to successfully perform the essential job functions. Reasonable accommodations may be made to enable individuals with disabilities to perform the essential functions. Frequency options consist of: Continuously, Frequently, Occasionally and Never.</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Physical Requirements</p><p>Hours Per Day</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Lifting Requirements</p><p>Frequency</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Sitting</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Lifting 0 - 15 lbs*</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Standing</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Lifting 16 â 50 lbs*</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Walking</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Lifting 51 - 100 lbs</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Stooping</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Lifting Over 100 lbs</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Crawling</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Kneeling</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Carrying Requirements</p><p>Frequency</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Bending</p><p>Hours</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Carrying 0 - 15 lbs*</p><p style="height:6px;"></p><p>Reaching (above your head)</p><p>Ho